{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "a9680735-3040-4e39-99c1-92a4c3bb8d2d", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/a9680735-3040-4e39-99c1-92a4c3bb8d2d@1.pkg/1772597661529/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597661873", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/a9680735-3040-4e39-99c1-92a4c3bb8d2d@1.pkg/1772597661529/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597661873"}, "identifier": "a9680735-3040-4e39-99c1-92a4c3bb8d2d", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}, {"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<p>本题考查法律的作用。</p>\n\n<p>A: 题干未涉及法律是判断是非曲直的标尺，故A不符合题意。</p>\n\n<p>B:《噪声污染防治法》实施后，广场音响、邻里装修、手机外放等噪音问题得到改善，营造了和谐安宁的社会环境。这体现了法律维护社会税序，保护社会公共利益，故B符合题意。</p>\n\n<p>C: 题干未提及法院用法治方式解决实际问题，故C不符合题意。</p>\n\n<p>D：法律并没有禁止广场舞和室内装修，D错误。</p>\n"}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<p>（改编）自《噪声污染防治法》施行以来，备受社会关注的广场音响、邻里装修、手机声音外放等社会热点问题得到有效改善，更好地营造了人民群众和谐安宁的生活环境。该法实施的效果表明（ &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;）</p>\n", "title": "（改编）自《噪声污染防治法》施行以来，备受社会关注的广场音响、邻里装修、手机声音外放等社会热点问题得到有效改善，更好地营造了人民群众和谐安宁的生活环境。该法实施的效果表明（     ）", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {"timer_type": "sequence"}, "time_dependent": false, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["B"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/a9680735-3040-4e39-99c1-92a4c3bb8d2d@1.pkg/item.json?v=1755143400603", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "ori